Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.

Einstein Discovery lets you Build Models, Manage and Deploy Models, Evaluate Model Quality, Compare Models, Deploy Models, Manage Prediction Definitions and Models.

You can also Analyze Prediction Accuracy with the Einstein Accuracy Analytics App, which helps monitor how well your models predict actual outcomes over time. Use insights from this app to fine-tune your models and produce better predictions.

Required user permissions are CRM Analytics Plus Admin permission set for creating and managing the Einstein Discovery for Sales app, and CRM Analytics Plus User permission set for using it.

The Einstein Accuracy Analytics App is not compatible with high-volume prediction writeback.
title: Improving Model Accuracy with Einstein Discovery
